h3.div: In the Princeville School District, all students experience success and reach their full academic and social potential. High expectations drive innovative educational strategies, strong academics, exceptional career and technical education programs, and diverse extracurricular activities.

li.em: implement transformative uses of technology while developing digital citizenship
develop and utilize skills and habits to realize full and unique human potential
be self-directed, produce and own knowledge, and positively contribute to society
embrace opportunities to explore interests, passions, and talents through the school, community, and world
